N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 365.2 - Applicability

State Regulations

This Part is applicable to the supervision of any
individual designated a Level 2 or 3 sex offender pursuant to the Sex Offender

Registration Act (SORA) and sentenced to a period of
probation. Notes
